milestones.description: Shaiman Anwar and Rizwan's 100-run partnership is UAE's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 91 between Rameez Shahzad and Usman
Paras Khadka and Malla's 62-run partnership is NEP's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 29 between Paras Khadka and Khakurel
Paras Khadka and Rohit Paudel's 54-run partnership is NEP's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 24 between Sompal Kami and Aarif Sheikh
Sompal Kami and Aarif Sheikh's 40-run partnership is NEP's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 23 between Sompal Kami and Aarif Sheikh
Paras Khadka has scored 2 fifty-plus scores in ODIs, the most for NEP breaking Khakurel's record
This is the highest match aggregate (509) involving teams U.A.E. & Nepal in ODIs
Paras Khadka's 115 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for NEP), surpassing Sompal Kami's 61
Paras Khadka has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (66) in an innings in ODIs for NEP, going past Sompal Kami's 38
Paras Khadka has become the top scorer for NEP in ODIs with 235 runs, going past Sompal Kami's 120
Karan KC has broken the record for most ducks (2) in ODIs for NEP, going past Basant Regmi's 2
Aarif Sheikh has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (6) for NEP, going past Airee
